casebody.data:
Anthony JONES, petitioner,
v.
Michael LEMKE, Warden. No. 13-8620. Supreme Court of the United States April 21, 2014.

Case below, 2013 WL 3787876.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Appellate Court of Illinois, Fourth District, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
